Horror crash claims at least 13 lives in Randfontein
A taxi collided with a truck on the R41 in Randfontein this afternoon.
JOHANNESBURG - Paramedics say there are multiple fatalities after a taxi collided with a truck on the R41 in Randfontein this afternoon.
It's understood at least 13 people have been killed.
According to Arrive Alive, one other person is in a critical condition.
Netcare 911's Athlenda Mathe says, "The exact details as to the cause of the accident will remain subject to a police investigation. Netcare 911 and other services are on the scene. The road has been cordoned off."
Motorists have been advised to avoid the R41.